div(class="flex min-h-full flex-col justify-center px-6 py-12 lg:px-8")
    div(class="sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-sm")
        div(class="flex justify-center")
            div(class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-600 text-white")
                svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg", fill="none", viewBox="0 0 24 24", stroke-width="1.5", stroke="currentColor", class="size-7")
                    path(stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round", d="m21 7.5-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9")
        h2(class="mt-6 text-center text-xl font-bold text-gray-900") 서비스 로그인
        p(class="mt-2 text-center text-[13px] text-gray-500") 계정 정보를 입력하여 로그인하세요.

    div(class="mt-8 sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-sm")
        div(class="space-y-5")
            div
                label(class="block text-[13px] font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1") 이메일
                input(
                    type="email",
                    autocomplete="email",
                    [(ngModel)]="data.email",
                    placeholder="name@example.com",
                    class="block w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] text-gray-900 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:outline-none")

            div
                label(class="block text-[13px] font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1") 비밀번호
                input(
                    type="password",
                    autocomplete="current-password",
                    [(ngModel)]="data.password",
                    (keyup.enter)="login()",
                    placeholder="비밀번호 입력",
                    class="block w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] text-gray-900 placeholder:text-gray-400 focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:outline-none")

            button(
                (click)="login()",
                class="flex w-full justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 px-3 py-2.5 text-[13px] font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600 transition-colors")
                | 로그인

        p(class="mt-8 text-center text-xs text-gray-400") &copy; 2026 Sample Service. All rights reserved.
